BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:NUTCRACKER! Magical Christmas Ballet
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20261223T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20261223T163000
DTSTAMP:20260710T043905Z
UID:occ-1717@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Dance Performance
DESCRIPTION:Tchaikovsky's Nutcracker as touring spectacle: international d
 ancers\, acrobatics\, and towering puppets.\n\nThe familiar Nutcracker sto
 ry\, set to Tchaikovsky's score: Clara\, a Christmas Eve gift\, and a drea
 m that carries her into a candy-bright kingdom. This touring production bi
 lls itself as North America's largest Nutcracker\, with an international c
 ast\, acrobatics\, and towering puppets sharing the stage.
GEO:33.7726136;-84.3853395
LAST-MODIFIED:20260710T043457Z
LOCATION:Fox Theatre\, 660 Peachtree St NE
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://foxtheatre.evenue.net/cgi-bin/ncommerce3/SEGetEventList?groupC
 ode=NUT&linkID=fta&shopperContext=&caller=&appCode=
END:VEVENT
